Package scrabble

Enum Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Tile>
      • scrabble.Tile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Tile>
    public enum Tile
extends java.lang.Enum<Tile>
    Tile represents an unplaced tile inside the Pool

    This enum is not appropriate for placed tiles, as it does not associate a symbol with the wildcard BLANK enum.
